<p>This week&#8217;s guest is Rajesh Thiharie &#8211; one of Australia&#8217;s more connected LinkedIn users &#8211; and a real life &#8216;Success Story&#8217; in using social networks to business benefit.</p>
<p>What is interesting about Rajesh and the experiences he recounts is the fact that 2 of the last 3 jobs Rajesh has had have come about as a direct result &#8230;<strong> <a href="http://tinyurl.com/RajeshThiharie">More</a></strong></p>
