<p>As sponsor of Australia&#8217;s first face-to-face Networking Event for LinkedIn users, Rob talks about the subsequent business benefits arising from this &#8211; as well as strategies for businesses and individuals &#8230; <strong><a href="http://tinyurl.com/RobKingma">More</a></strong></p>
