<p>Regular followers of this show will be familiar with the challenge given to me by Cameron Reilly (CEO of TPN &amp; host of the G&#8217;Day World show), that kicked it all off to begin with &#8211; and the subsequent challenge that I made to HIM, back in Episode #001.</p>
