<p>One of the themes that has emerged from conversations with my guests over the past few weeks has been about how Social Networks offer marketers the opportunity of engaging with consumers in a way that is not intrusive, but relevant &#8211; sometimes even welcome.</p>
<p>Ian Lyons is Business Development Director at pureprofile &#8211; a permission-based marketing company &#8230; <strong><a href="http://tinyurl.com/IanLyons">More</a></strong></p>
