<p><strong><a title="Connections #019 - I'm on LinkedIn - Now What?" href="http://tinyurl.com/JasonAlba">Connections #019 &#8211; I&#8217;m on LinkedIn &#8211; Now What?</a></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/JasonAlba"><img title="Jason Alba" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2259/2221497077_7ddbd3757f_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Jason Alba" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a></p>
<p>Jason Alba is Chief Executive Officer of JibberJobber.com &#8211; a leading Job Search Management Tool.</p>
<p>He&#8217;s also the author of a book on how to use LinkedIn more effectively, entitled &#8216;I&#8217;m on LinkedIn &#8211; Now What?&#8217; Jason is a smart guy &#8211; with an easy conversational style and a ready chuckle. &#8230; <strong><a href="http://tinyurl.com/JasonAlba">More</a></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3270/2889203278_786e30a369.jpg" alt="" vspace="5" width="640" height="1" /></p>
<p><strong><a title="Connections #020 - 10,000 Contacts - Now What?" href="http://tinyurl.com/StevenBurda">Connections #020 &#8211; 10,000 Contacts &#8211; Now What?</a></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://tinyurl.com/StevenBurda"><img title="Steven Burda" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2032/2222304570_8d002d2e17_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Steven Burda" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a></p>
<p>Steven Burda is a young Entrepreneur &amp; Senior Financial Analyst with a Fortune 500 company.</p>
<p>He&#8217;s also one of the Top 50 most-connected LinkedIn&#8217;s users, according to TopLinked.com. As a 26-year old who has yet to realize any significant commercial benefit from his 10,000+ connections, Steven is a classic case of &#8230;<strong> <a href="http://tinyurl.com/StevenBurda">More</a></strong></p>
