		<title>Connections #055 &#8211; Synchronizing Web Pages with Audio</title>
		<link>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2009/05/03/connections-055-synchronizing-web-pages-with-audio/</link>
		<comments>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2009/05/03/connections-055-synchronizing-web-pages-with-audio/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2009 05:20:19 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Stan Relihan</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Business]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[General]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Internet]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LinkedIn]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Marketing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Networking]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Podcast]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Social Networking]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Stan Relihan]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web 2.0]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Business Collaboration]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CynoCast]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Publishing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Robert Hayes]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Sales Tool]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Webcast]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/?p=574</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Robert Hayes is an entrepreneur and developer, based in Denver, Colorado &#8211; and the Principal &#38; President of CynoCast, the software company he founded. CynoCast is an innovative solution that allows you to deliver targeted web pages immediately to a another person&#8217;s browser, while you&#8217;re talking to them, via telephone, Skype, embedded VOIP or Instant [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/roberthayes" target="_new"><img title="Robert Hayes" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3357/3495430027_a38566a055_o_d.png" border="0" alt="Robert Hayes" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/roberthayes" target="_new">Robert Hayes</a></strong> is an entrepreneur and developer, based in Denver, Colorado &#8211; and the Principal &amp; President of CynoCast, the software company he founded.</p>
<p>CynoCast is an innovative solution that allows you to deliver targeted web pages immediately to a another person&#8217;s browser, while you&#8217;re talking to them, via telephone, Skype, embedded VOIP or Instant Messaging application.</p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/audio/cynocast.htm">Click here to see it in action, via a special &#8216;CynoCast-enhanced&#8217; version of this Episode.</a></strong></p>
<p>An avid sports fan, Robert was inspired to develop his product while watching a sports game &#8211; and thought it would be great if the announcers could bring up a player&#8217;s statistics and display them on the screen, during the broadcast.</p>
<p>Since then, in addition to creating a more interactive experience for their TV &amp; radio viewers and listeners, CynoCast has developed into a powerful sales and business collaboration tool, because of its ability to provide an enriched, interactive element to conversations &#8211; either in real time, or pre-recorded.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Web Links:</strong></span><br />
<a href="http://www.cynocast.com" target="_new"><strong>CynoCast.com</strong></a> &#8211; CynoCast web site<br />
<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/roberthayes" target="_new"><strong>LinkedIn</strong></a> &#8211; Robert&#8217;s LinkedIn profile<br />
<a href="http://twitter.com/CynoCast" target="_new"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> &#8211; CynoCast on Twitter</p>
