		<itunes:subtitle>Robert Hayes is an entrepreneur and developer, based in Denver, Colorado - and the Principal &#38; President of CynoCast, the software company he founded.

CynoCast is ...</itunes:subtitle>
		<itunes:summary>Robert Hayes is an entrepreneur and developer, based in Denver, Colorado - and the Principal &#38; President of CynoCast, the software company he founded.

CynoCast is an innovative solution that allows you to deliver targeted web pages immediately to a another person's browser, while you're talking to them, via telephone, Skype, embedded VOIP or Instant Messaging application.



Click here to see it in action, via a special 'CynoCast-enhanced' version of this Episode.

An avid sports fan, Robert was inspired to develop his product while watching a sports game - and thought it would be great if the announcers could bring up a player's statistics and display them on the screen, during the broadcast.

Since then, in addition to creating a more interactive experience for their TV &#38; radio viewers and listeners, CynoCast has developed into a powerful sales and business collaboration tool, because of its ability to provide an enriched, interactive element to conversations - either in real time, or pre-recorded.

Web Links:
CynoCast.com - CynoCast web site
LinkedIn - Robert's LinkedIn profile
Twitter - CynoCast on Twitter
 


