		<title>Connections #047 &#8211; Road Rules: Be the Truck. Not the Squirrel</title>
		<link>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2009/01/04/connections-047-road-rules-be-the-truck-not-the-squirrel/</link>
		<comments>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2009/01/04/connections-047-road-rules-be-the-truck-not-the-squirrel/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 04 Jan 2009 05:17:19 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Stan Relihan</dc:creator>
