<a href="http://johnmccrea.myplaxo.com/" target="_new"><strong>John McCrea&#8217;s Plaxo profile</strong></a><br />
<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/0/11/581" target="_new"><strong>John McCrea&#8217;s LinkedIn profile</strong></a></p>
