		<title>Connections #041 &#8211; Blocking the Hacker Attacks</title>
		<link>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2008/10/04/connections-041-blocking-the-hacker-attacks/</link>
		<comments>http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/2008/10/04/connections-041-blocking-the-hacker-attacks/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 04 Oct 2008 10:24:07 +0000</pubDate>
