		<description><![CDATA[Bart Jellema is a highly-accomplished Web 2.0 Software Developer, Database Architect and Ajax expert &#8211; originally from the Netherlands, now living in Sydney, Australia. Bart&#8217;s now put his money where his mouth is and become an Entrepreneur &#8211; using his software skills &#38; Internet knowledge to launch Tjoos.com, a new Online Coupon Aggregator &#38; Price [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/bartjellema" target="_new"><img title="Bart Jellema" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3061/2746540420_99bce5a886_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Bart Jellema" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/bartjellema" target="_new">Bart Jellema</a> </strong>is a highly-accomplished Web 2.0 Software Developer, Database Architect and <strong><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AJAX">Ajax</a></strong> expert &#8211; originally from the Netherlands, now living in Sydney, Australia.</p>
<p>Bart&#8217;s now put his money where his mouth is and become an Entrepreneur &#8211; using his software skills &amp; Internet knowledge to launch <strong><a href="http://www.tjoos.com/" target="_new">Tjoos.com</a></strong>, a new Online Coupon Aggregator &amp; Price Comparison site that (less that a year since its launch) is attracting hundreds of thousands of unique visitors every month.<br />
</p>
<p>In this lively and informative conversation, Bart discusses some of the fundamental principles of <strong><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Search_engine_optimization" target="_new">Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</a></strong> that he&#8217;s successfully utilized to catapult <strong><a href="http://www.tjoos.com/" target="_new">Tjoos.com</a></strong> to commercially viability in just 9 months.</p>
