			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/octaviopitaluganeto" target="_new"><img title="Octavio Pitaluga Neto" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3253/2593189296_589654f690.jpg" border="0" alt="Octavio Pitaluga Neto" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/octaviopitaluganeto" target="_new">Octavio Pitaluga Neto</a> </strong>is a successful Networker, Public Speaker, Entrepreneur and <strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/octaviopitaluganeto">Chief Networking Officer</a></strong> with <strong><a href="http://www.topexecutivesnet.com" target="_new">Top Executives Net (TEN)</a></strong>.</p>
<p>Located in Brazil, Octavio has one of the largest LinkedIn networks in the world &#8211; and the largest in Latin America (and <strong><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ibero-America" target="_new">Ibero-America</a></strong>).</p>
<p>In this conversation, Octavio discusses his approach to networking, and the benefits of having a large &amp; visible Personal Brand.<br />
<br />
He also shares a few of the techniques he&#8217;s employed in building his network &#8211; and outlines the vision for <strong><a href="http://www.topexecutivesnet.com" target="_new">Top Executives Net</a></strong>, the new Business Accelerator platform he&#8217;s created (and for which he is currently seeking international partners).</p>
