			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.sixdegreesfromdave.com" target="_new"><img title="Dave Mendoza" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2179/2369504599_0abbc5e29d.jpg" border="0" alt="Dave Mendoza" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.sixdegreesfromdave.com" target="_top">Dave Mendoza</a></strong> is a Contract Recruiter, Sourcer &amp; Trainer located in Denver, Colorado.</p>
