		<description><![CDATA[Doug Hughes is Vice President, Customer Services for Australia &#38; New Zealand at Oracle Corporation. Doug was the Keynote Speaker on the subject of &#8216;Sales Performance &#38; Improvement&#8216; at a recent Networking Event, organized by myself and my colleagues at Expert Executive Search &#8211; in conjunction with our business associates from Oracle, Hewlett Packard &#38; [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/0/688/38b" target="_new"><img title="Doug Hughes" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2387/2287129851_83e512d305_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Doug Hughes" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/0/688/38b" target="_top">Doug Hughes</a> </strong>is Vice President, Customer Services for Australia &amp; New Zealand at <strong><a href="http://www.oracle.com" target="_new">Oracle Corporation</a></strong>.</p>
<p>Doug was the Keynote Speaker on the subject of &#8216;<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24082511@N08/sets/72157603958067212/show/" target="_new"><strong>Sales Performance &amp; Improvement</strong></a>&#8216; at a recent <strong><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/show/" target="_new">Networking Event</a></strong>, organized by myself and my colleagues at <strong><a href="http://www.expertsearch.com.au" target="_new">Expert Executive Search</a></strong> &#8211; in conjunction with our business associates from <strong><a href="http://www.oracle.com" target="_new">Oracle</a></strong>, <strong><a href="http://www.hp.com" target="_new">Hewlett Packard</a></strong> &amp; <strong><a href="http://www.ey-rgrs.com/" target="_new">Ernst &amp; Young Revenue Growth Services</a></strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="The crowd listens intently to the presentation" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/2295230399/in/set-72157603997687539/" target="_new"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3074/2295230399_9a17296b09_s.jpg" border="0" alt="The crowd listen intently to the presentation" hspace="1" width="37" height="37" /></a><a title="Rob Kingma, Senior Manager with Ernst &amp; Young's Revenue Growth Services" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/2295230395/in/set-72157603997687539/" target="_new"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3220/2295230395_495c2f0153_s.jpg" border="0" alt="Rob Kingma, Senior Manager with Ernst &amp; Young's Revenue Growth Services" hspace="1" width="37" height="37" /></a><a title="Gary Mitchell, Managing Director, Enterasys" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/2295230393/in/set-72157603997687539/" target="_new"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3112/2295230393_36c964f898_s.jpg" border="0" alt="Gary Mitchell, Managing Director, Enterasys" hspace="1" width="37" height="37" /></a><a title="The crowd listens intently to the presentation" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/2296019164/in/set-72157603997687539/" target="_new"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3043/2296019164_e4092840ab_s.jpg" border="0" alt="The crowd listens intently to the presentation" hspace="1" width="37" height="37" /></a><a title="Doug Hughes, Oracle Vice President - Customer Services for Australia &amp; New Zealand outlines some of the leading Soacial Applications, such as Google, WebX, MySpace, facebook, Digg, LinkedIn &amp; Spock" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/24095894@N04/2296019160/in/set-72157603997687539/" target="_new"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3013/2296019160_06ab3638e9_s.jpg" border="0" alt="Doug Hughes, Oracle Vice President - Customer Services for Australia &amp; New Zealand outlines some of the leading Soacial Applications, such as Google, WebX, My