			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/robkingma" target="_new"><img title="Rob Kingma" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3076/2862203940_62dd6499ef_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Rob Kingma" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/robkingma" target="_new"><strong>Rob Kingma</strong></a> is a Senior Manager with <a href="http://www.ey-rgrs.com" target="_new"><strong>Ernst &amp; Young Revenue Growth Services</strong></a> in Sydney, Australia.</p>
