		<description><![CDATA[John Johnston is a Digital Interactive Designer &#38; Art Director working in Sydney, Australia &#8211; and an enthusiast of a number of Social Media networks. In this episode, John talks about his latest passion, Twitter &#8211; new kid on the block among social networks, whose main point of difference seems to be the brevity of [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/jjprojects" target="_new"><img title="John Johnston" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3020/2376372635_a68b3e828c_m.jpg" border="0" alt="John Johnston" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a><strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/jjprojects" target="_top">John Johnston</a></strong> is a Digital Interactive Designer &amp; Art Director working in Sydney, Australia &#8211; and an enthusiast of a number of Social Media networks.</p>
<p>In this episode, John talks about his latest passion, <strong><a href="http://twitter.com/" target="_top">Twitter</a></strong> &#8211; new kid on the block among social networks, whose main point of difference seems to be the brevity of messages exchanged between it members (think micro-communication).</p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.jjprojects.net/" target="_top">John</a></strong> is an avid enthusiast who enjoys <strong><a href="http://twitter.com/jjprojects" target="_top">making new contacts</a></strong> &#8211; with a new Generation X &#8216;multitasking&#8217; perspective, as he likes to make use of a number of different Social Networking tools simultaneously.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.feedburner.com/fb/a/emailverifySubmit?feedId=1560722" target="_new"><img title="Subscribe via E-mail" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3068/2918643244_1edc7777a2_o_d.png" border="0" alt="Subscribe via E-mail" vspace="0" width="143" height="26" /></a> <a href="itpc://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/feed/" target="_new"><img title="Subscribe via iTunes" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3098/2918643246_e5c1d11959_o_d.png" border="0" alt="Subscribe via iTunes" vspace="0" width="143" height="26" /></a><br />
<a href="http://try.chalk.com/connections" target="_new"><img title="Subscribe via BlackBerry" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3098/2918643240_cc95cf409f_o_d.png" border="0" alt="Subscribe via BlackBerry" vspace="0" width="180" height="35" /></a><br />
<a href="http://connections.thepodcastnetwork.com/feed/" target="_new"><img title="Add RSS feed" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3277/2918643242_4f315c383b_o.png" border="0" alt="Add RSS feed" vspace="3" width="275" height="25" /></a></p>
