		<itunes:subtitle>John Johnston is a Digital Interactive Designer &#38; Art Director working in Sydney, Australia - and an enthusiast of a number of Social Media networks.

In ...</itunes:subtitle>
		<itunes:summary>John Johnston is a Digital Interactive Designer &#38; Art Director working in Sydney, Australia - and an enthusiast of a number of Social Media networks.

In this episode, John talks about his latest passion, Twitter - new kid on the block among social networks, whose main point of difference seems to be the brevity of messages exchanged between it members (think micro-communication).



John is an avid enthusiast who enjoys making new contacts - with a new Generation X 'multitasking' perspective, as he likes to make use of a number of different Social Networking tools simultaneously.
 


