			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/cmayaud" target="_new"><img title="Christian Mayaud" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2125/2302877705_a9c78f013c_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Christian Mayaud" hspace="5" width="90" height="90" align="left" /></a>This week&#8217;s guest is <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/cmayaud" target="_new"><strong>Christian Mayaud</strong></a> &#8211; a successful Venture Capitalist whose amazing Rolodex formed part of the initial nucleus of <strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com" target="_new">LinkedIn</a></strong> users.</p>
<p>He&#8217;s also founder of the <a href="http://themetanetwork.com/" target="_new"><strong>LinkedIn LIONs</strong></a> and one of LinkedIn&#8217;s most highly-connected users.<br />
<br />
In this interview, Christian shares his insights on the early days of <strong><a href="http://www.linkedin.com" target="_new">LinkedIn</a></strong>, High Performance Networking and the Future of Networking.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>WEB LINKS:</strong></span></p>
